# Tech Stack Reference

## Core Framework

- **Next.js 14** - App Router, Server Components, Middleware
- **React 18** - Latest React features
- **TypeScript 5** - Strict type checking

## UI & Styling

- **shadcn/ui** - Component library (Radix UI primitives)
- **Tailwind CSS 3.4.17** - Utility-first CSS with CSS variables
- **Lucide React** - Icon library
- **next-themes** - Dark mode support
- **React Icons** - Additional icon library

## State & Data

- **Zustand latest** - Lightweight state management
- **Convex 1.28.0** - Backend-as-a-service (database, queries, mutations, actions)
- **React Hook Form** - Form handling (if used)
- **Zod** - Schema validation (if used)
- **Immer latest** - Immutable state updates

## Visualization

- **Recharts 2.15.3** - Charts and graphs
- **D3 Scale** - Data transformations (if needed)

## Utilities

- **date-fns latest** - Date manipulation
- **Sonner** - Toast notifications (via shadcn/ui - Radix UI Toast)
- **@dnd-kit** - Drag and drop functionality
- **PostHog 1.281.0** - Analytics and event tracking
- **Motion 12.23.24** - Animation library
- **React Day Picker** - Date picker component
- **React Resizable Panels** - Resizable panel layouts
- **Vaul** - Drawer component
- **xlsx** - Excel export (if needed - not currently in package.json)
- **html-to-image** - Export to images (if needed - not currently in package.json)

## Development Tools

- **ESLint 9** - Linting
- **Prettier 3.5.3** - Code formatting
- **Husky 9.1.7** - Git hooks
- **lint-staged** - Pre-commit checks

## Package Manager

- **pnpm** - Primary package manager (see package.json for version)

## Important Notes

- All UI components from shadcn/ui are in `components/ui/`
- Convex handles all backend operations (queries, mutations, actions)
- Zustand is used for client-side UI state management
- React Hook Form + Zod can be used for form handling and validation (if needed)
- PostHog is integrated for analytics tracking

